en: Your progress will be permanently deleted and cannot be recovered.
be: Ваш прагрэс будзе назаўсёды выдалены і не можа быць адноўлены.

en: A fun flag quiz game with an emphasis on often overlooked languages.
What language would you like to use?
This can be changed anytime in the settings menu.
